2020年8月22日，一架由{{le|西南航空 (南苏丹)|South West Aviation (South Sudan)|南苏丹西南航空}}运营的[[安东诺夫国营公司|安托诺夫]][[安-26|安-26]]运输机在该国[[朱巴国际机场|朱巴国际机场]]起飞时发生事故，机上共9人中有8人罹难、1人生还。

==背景==
西南航空成立于2017年，旗下的一架[[Let_L-410|Let L-410]]飞机曾于2018年{{Le|2018年伊罗勒L-410坠毁事故|Yirol Let L-410 Turbolet crash|发生一起事故}}，造成20人死亡。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Crash: South West Aviation L410 at Yirol on Sep 9th 2018, impacted lake on approach to Yirol City|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=4bd74c51|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=avherald.com|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028130403/http://avherald.com/h?article=4bd74c51|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年4月，南苏丹总统[[萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特|萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特]]禁止机龄20年以上的飞机在该国执行客运业务。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=17 people killed in plane crash in South Sudan|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-08/22/c_139310179.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-08-22|format=|publisher=新华网|language=|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901205010/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-08/22/c_139310179.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事故过程==
据目击者报告，本次涉事飞机起飞后不久失去动力，在朱巴国际机场附近的居民区坠落。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=An-26 Cargo Plane Crashes After Takeoff In South Sudan|url=https://simpleflying.com/juba-an-26-crash/|accessdate=2020-10-28|date=2020-08-22|work=Simple Flying|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921125240/https://simpleflying.com/juba-an-26-crash/|dead-url=no}}</ref>事故不太可能是天气恶劣导致。<ref name=":1" />初步报道称有7～17人身亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=South Sudan: 7 killed in plane crash shortly after Juba takeoff|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/8/22/south-sudan-7-killed-in-plane-crash-shortly-after-juba-takeoff|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103162337/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/8/22/south-sudan-7-killed-in-plane-crash-shortly-after-juba-takeoff|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1名幸存者被送往医院，情况危殆<ref>{{Cite web|title=At Least 17 Dead After Plane Crash in South Sudan|url=https://samchui.com/2020/08/22/at-least-17-dead-after-plane-crash-in-south-sudan/|accessdate=2020-10-28|date=2020-08-22|last=Perton|first=Ted|work=SamChui.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917042249/https://samchui.com/2020/08/22/at-least-17-dead-after-plane-crash-in-south-sudan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。南苏丹交通运输部长表示机上有5名机组人员，均为俄罗斯籍。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Seven killed after cargo plane crashes after takeoff in South Sudan|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/aug/23/seven-killed-after-cargo-plane-crashes-after-takeoff-in-south-sudan-2187092.html|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=The New Indian Express|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824082833/https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/aug/23/seven-killed-after-cargo-plane-crashes-after-takeoff-in-south-sudan-2187092.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>事故早期的报道称飞机在居民接近时起火。<ref>{{Cite web|title=17 killed as plane crashes after takeoff from Juba airport|url=https://www.nation.co.ke/kenya/news/africa/17-killed-as-plane-crashes-after-takeoff-from-juba-airport-1923796|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Daily Nation|language=|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825195305/https://www.nation.co.ke/kenya/news/africa/17-killed-as-plane-crashes-after-takeoff-from-juba-airport-1923796|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一些媒体报道本机是联合国[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]的包机<ref>{{Cite web|title=South West Aviation Antonov An-26 at Juba on Aug 22nd 2020, lost height after departure|url=https://www.aeroinside.com/item/14851/south-west-aviation-an26-at-juba-on-aug-22nd-2020-lost-height-after-departure|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=www.aeroinside.com|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031080204/https://www.aeroinside.com/item/14851/south-west-aviation-an26-at-juba-on-aug-22nd-2020-lost-height-after-departure|dead-url=no}}</ref>，机上载有多余部件、摩托车、食物和[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]的人员工资等<ref name=":1" />。但世界粮食计划署随后澄清本机实为南苏丹一家公司承包，服务联合国旗下诸多组织。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WFP denies chartering cargo plane that crashed in Juba|url=https://radiotamazuj.org/en/news/article/wfp-denies-chartering-cargo-plane-that-crashed-in-juba|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=Radio Tamazuj|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016042521/https://radiotamazuj.org/en/news/article/wfp-denies-chartering-cargo-plane-that-crashed-in-juba|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 各方反应 ==
南苏丹总统萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特要求该国交通运输部在评估航机的适航性时“遵守国际标准”，还表示“应对如此悲剧的难度可想而知，但我们要一起努力找出事故的原因，吸取教训，防止类似的事件再次发生”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kiir sends condolences to families of plane crash victims|url=https://radiotamazuj.org/en/news/article/kiir-sends-condolences-to-families-of-plane-crash-victims|accessdate=2020-10-28|work=Radio Tamazuj|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824233347/https://radiotamazuj.org/en/news/article/kiir-sends-condolences-to-families-of-plane-crash-victims|dead-url=no}}</ref>

